[!] 17 Jul 2013, random - Bug (0123967): Add To Cart Popup: Popup content was not destroyed after closing the popup. Fixed.
[!] 16 Jul 2013, random - Bug (0124017): Add To Cart Popup: Customizing its template with JavaScript code was making the popup to open multiple times. Fixed.
[!] 11 Jul 2013, random - Bug (0134402): Feature Comparison: "Compare selected" and "Add to comparison list" buttons were not working in some cases. Fixed.
[!] 27 Jun 2013, aim - Bug (0133449): Flyout Menus: Menu cache was not updated properly when a product's categories were changed on the product modify page.
