[*] 16 May 2013, aim - Improvement (0132598): Disabled MYSQL query_cache for DEVELOPMENT_MODE. long_query_time is now set to 5 sec.
[*] 15 May 2013, random - Improvement (1325320): Moved initialization for several modules from the init.php file to functions.
