[!] 30 May 2013, aim - Bug (0133203): There was an SQL error related to 'Compatibility with old product storage routine' feature. Fixed.
[!] 27 May 2013, random - Bug (0130963): func_secure_update_config_signatures called from func_register_admin_ip could be unavailable. Fixed.
